{"id":232651383,"title":"#分享 愛奇藝,滴滴打車中台設計","content":"最近中台的概念很火，所以就稍微了解一下來跟大家分享。在有中台這個概念之前呢？每間公司在推出新的業務的時候，都需要另外做屬於該業務的客服、金流、ETL等系統。而首先提出中台這個概念的是阿里巴巴，他們一開始是做 b2b 的服務，後來業務線越開越多條，自然也就遇到這個問題。\n \n \n 而他們靈光一閃，既然之前已經做過客服、金流，何不把它當成類似 infra 的模組放在底層跟其他業務共用？這樣公司 scale 的速度就會超快！\n \n \n 以下舉滴滴打車的中台當例子：\n http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/29abfafdb89f40e7b1403b39ba4180c6.jpg\n \n \n 爱奇艺的推荐中台寫得相當完整，給從事 Machine Learning 的朋友們參考：\n http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15c52983090c450683e4a046bfdfcb0f.jpg\n http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/3450b4b78df943ebb31c615e6bceefc1.jpg\n \n \n 最後附上原文：\n https://www.toutiao.com/a6751749635582198279/?tt_from=copy_link&utm_campaign=client_share&timestamp=1575819408&app=news_article&utm_source=copy_link&utm_medium=toutiao_ios&req_id=201912082336480100260772031198BA1A&group_id=6751749635582198279","excerpt":"最近中台的概念很火，所以就稍微了解一下來跟大家分享。在有中台這個概念之前呢？每間公司在推出新的業務的時候，都需要另外做屬於該業務的客服、金流、ETL等系統。而首先提出中台這個概念的是阿里巴巴，他們一開","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":false,"pinned":false,"forumId":"a6dc1b6b-0aca-4004-86c8-3af6cdbfad23","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2019-12-09T01:36:42.625Z","updatedAt":"2019-12-09T01:39:27.795Z","commentCount":5,"likeCount":4,"tags":[],"topics":["中台","愛奇藝","滴滴打車","架構設計"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":true,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"軟體工程師","forumAlias":"softwareengineer","school":"搜尋工程師 小david","department":"ggggghgggg","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":true,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":3},{"id":"aa0d425f-d530-4478-9a77-fe3aedc79eea","count":1}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/29abfafdb89f40e7b1403b39ba4180c6.jpg"},{"url":"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/15c52983090c450683e4a046bfdfcb0f.jpg"},{"url":"http://p3.pstatp.com/large/pgc-image/3450b4b78df943ebb31c615e6